  <content>
    <chapter line="1">Tanādayo <pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0028" /></chapter>
    <hangnum line="2" number="120"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="3"> Tanu vitthāre saka sattismiṃ-du paritāpe sanu dānasmiṃ,</gatha1>
    <gatha2 line="4">Vana yācāyaṃ manu bodhasmiṃ-hi gate apa pāpuṇanasmiṃ (hi,)</gatha2>
    <gathalast line="5">Kara karaṇasmiṃ(bhavati)si bandhe-su abhissavane(tanu ādīni;)</gathalast>
    <centered line="6">Niccaṃ ṇeṇayantā curādayo.</centered>
    <hangnum line="7" number="121"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="8"> Cura theyye loka (dhātu) dassane aki lakkhaṇe,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="9">Siyā thaka patighāte (puna) takka vitakkaṇe;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="10" number="122"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="11"> Lakkha dassanaaṅkesu (vattate) makkha makkhaṇe,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="12">Bhakkhā’dane mokkha moce sukha-dukkha (ca) takiraye;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="13" number="123"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0029" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="14"> Liṅga cittakirayā’dīsu maga-magga gavesane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="15">(Punā’pi) paca vitthāre klese vañca palambhane.</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="16" number="124"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="17"> Vacca ajjhāyane acca pūjāyaṃ vaca bhāsane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="18">Raca patiyatane suca pesuññe ruca rocane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="19" number="125"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="20"> Mucappamocane loca dassane kaca dittiyaṃ,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="21">Sajjā’jja ajjane tajja tajjane vajja vajjane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="22" number="126"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="23"> Yuja saṃyamane pūja pūjāyaṃ tija tejane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="24">Paja magga saṃvaraṇe gate bhaja vibhājane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="25" number="127"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="26"> (Atho) bhāja puthakkāre sabhāja pītidassane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="27">(Atho tu) ghaṭa saṅghāte ghaṭṭa sañcalanā’disu;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="28" number="128"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0030" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="29"> Kuṭa-koṭṭacchedane (dve) kuṭa ākoṭanā’disu,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="30">Naṭa nacce caṭa-puṭa bhede vaṇṭa vibhājane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="31" number="129"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="32"> Tuvaṭṭa ekasayane ghaṭo visaraṇe (siyā),</gatha1>
    <gatha2 line="33">Guṇṭha oguṇṭhane heṭha bādhāyaṃ veṭha veṭhane</gatha2>
    <gathalast line="34">Guḍi veṭhe kaḍi-khaḍi bhedane maḍi bhūsane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="35" number="130"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="36"> Paṇḍa-bhaṇḍa paribhāse daḍi āṇāya (mīrito),</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="37">Taḍi saṃtāḷane piṇḍa saṅghāte chaḍḍa chaḍḍane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="38" number="131"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="39"> Vaṇṇa saṃvaṇṇane cuṇṇa cuṇṇane āṇa pesane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="40">Gaṇa saṃkalane kaṇṇa savaṇe cinta cintane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="41" number="132"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="42"> Santa saṅkocane manta gutta bhāsana jānane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="43">Cita saṃcetanā’disu kitta saṃsaddane (bhave;)</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="44" number="133"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0031" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="45"> Yata nīyyātane gantha sandabbhe attha yācane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="46">Katha vākyappabandhe (ca) vida ñāṇe nude cuda;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="47" number="134"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="48"> Chadā’pavāraṇe chadda vamane chanda icchayaṃ,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="49">Vadī’bhivāda thomesu bhadikalyāṇakammani;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="50" number="135"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="51"> Hiḷāda (tu) sukhe gandha sūcane vidha kampane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="52">Randha pāke (atho) māna pūjāyaṃ nu tthutimhi (tu;)</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="53" number="136"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="54"> Thana devasadde ūna parihāne thena coriye,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="55">Dhana sadde ñapa tosa nisāna māraṇā’disu;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="56" number="137"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="57"> Lapa vākye jhapa dāhe rupa ropaṇaādisu,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="58">Pī tappane (siyā) kappa vitakke labhi vañcane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="59" number="138"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0032" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="60"> (Atho) vahi garahāyaṃ samu sāntvana dassane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="61">Kamu icchāya kantimhi (siyā) thoma silāghane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="62" number="139"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="63"> Timu temana saṅkāsu ama rogagatā’disu,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="64">Saṃgāma yuddhe (vatteyya) īra vācā pakampane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="65" number="140"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="66"> Vara āvaraṇi’cchāsu yācāyaṃ dhara dhāraṇe,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="67">Tīra kamma samattimhi pāra sāmatthiyā’disu;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="68" number="141"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="69"> Tulu’mmāne khala sove sañcaye pālarakkhaṇe,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="70">Kala saṅkalanā’dīsu (bhave) mīla nimīlane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="71" number="142"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="72"> Sīlū’padhāraṇe mūla rohaṇe lala icchane,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="73">Dula ukkhepaṇe pūla mahattana samussaye;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="74" number="143"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0033" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="75"> Ghusa sadde pisa pese bhusā’laṅkaraṇe (siyā,)</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="76">Rusa pārusiye khuṃsa akkose pusa posane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="77" number="144"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="78"> Disa uccāraṇā’dīsu vasa acchādane (siyā,)</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="79">Rasa’ssāde rave snehe (atho) sisa visesane;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="80" number="145"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="81"> Si bandhe missa sammisse kuha vimbhāpane siyā,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="82">Raha cāge gate (cā’pi) maha pūjāya (mīrito;)</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="83" number="146"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="84"> Pihi’cchāyaṃ siyā vīḷa lajjāyaṃ eḷa phāḷane</gatha1>
    <gatha2 line="85">Hīḷa gārahiye pīḷa bādhāyaṃ taḷa tāḷane</gatha2>
    <gathalast line="86">Laḷa (dhātū)’pasevā’yaṃ (vattatī’mecurādayo;)</gathalast>
    <centered line="87">Samattā sattagaṇā.</centered>
    <hangnum line="88" number="147"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0034" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="89"> Bhuvādī ca rudhādī ca-divādi svā’dayo gaṇā,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="90">Kiyādī ca tanādī ca-curādītī’dha sattadhā;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="91" number="148"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="92"> Kirayāvācittamakkhātu-me’kekattho bahū’dito,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="93">Payogato’nugantabbā-anekatthā hi dhātavo;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="94" number="149"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="95"> Hitāya mandabuddhīnaṃ-vyattaṃ vaṇṇakkamā lahuṃ,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="96">Racitā dhātumañjusā-sīlavaṃsena dhīmatā;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="97" number="150"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="98"> Saddhammapaṅkeruharājahaṃso,</gatha1>
    <gatha2 line="99">Āsiṭṭhadhammaṭṭhiti sīlavaṃso;</gatha2>
    <gatha3 line="100">Yakkhaddilenākhya nivāsavāsī,</gatha3>
    <gathalast line="101">Yatissaro soyamidaṃ akāsi;</gathalast>
    <centered line="102">Kaccāyana dhātumañjūsā samattā.</centered>
    <subhead line="103">Sācariyānusiṭṭhā <pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0035" /> parisiṭṭhaparibhāsā</subhead>
    <hangnum line="104" number="1"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="105"> Ekā nekassa rānantū-’bhayesaṃ antimā sarā,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="106">Aṅgānubandhā dhātūnaṃ-vuccante’pi yathākkamaṃ;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="107" number="2"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="108"> Dhātuno vyāñjanā pubbe-niggahītaṃ sama’ntimā,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="109">Ivaṇṇenā’rudhādīna-manubandhena ciṇhitaṃ;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="110" number="3"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="111"> Sesā’nubandhā sabbesaṃ-hontī’dhu’ccāraṇapphalā,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="112">Uccāvacapphalā bhāsa-ntarampatvā bha vanti’pi;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="113" number="4"><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0036" /></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="114"> Nāmadhātuka bhāvo’pi-kirayāya adhikārato,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="115">Viruddhantarābhāvā-kvacideva payujjate;</gathalast>
    <hangnum line="116" number="5"></hangnum>
    <gatha1 line="117"> Dvandayuttivasā kvāpi-ādeso yovibhattiyā,</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="118">Guṇādibhāva saddo’pi-takirayatthe vidhīyate;</gathalast>
